{"tid":332167,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得麥明詩越來越煩膠？","createTime":"2017-07-22T18:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T08:44:33.000Z","uid":14730,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b487a26ba89953ef2900fa2d8dde03618070a45","tid":332167,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/024537_14d023c95f3626526f44ed7cc9ad6bbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F024537_14d023c95f3626526f44ed7cc9ad6bbe.jpg&h=14b6f805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麥明詩昨日現身書展代母親領獎，被問到舊愛林作出書教用英文追女仔，可有捧場？麥明詩直言有看過，且一早已看過初稿，當時亦有給予意見。可覺得書中的案例招數似曾相識？她笑言﹕「我沒詳細看那些案例，費事去想對象是誰，大家都在英國讀書，都是朋友，大概都認識。（書中有一part說給最愛的人？）我研究過應該是他婆婆，不要對號入座，如果不是便很樣衰。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問會否考慮出書教識男仔？麥明詩笑言在這方面很被動，可能會教人如何婉轉拒絕追求者，她說﹕「我喜歡較婉轉的，不鍾意直接叫人『死開』。其實我都不是有很多機會練習，只是有些見解而已。」可會考慮推出寫真集？她表示寫真集都有很多類型，可以是很藝術性的。如果要性感？麥明詩笑指如果很藝術性是OK的。對於在《賭城群英會》中被指「死魚眼」？她也承認眼神是自己弱點，成日都在待機狀態：「之後會改進，我每日起身會練擘大隻眼10次。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ulbCE7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ulbCE7&d=3aNSw6jVxEDekNmPJGIa%2BMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=9bef9d46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ulbCE7</a>"},{"pid":"d3a8a566923544a23a9378fc54895171ec91c685","tid":332167,"uid":13504,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:48:36.000Z","msg":"覺, 又樣衰又臭格"},{"pid":"146dc4e14e6e02c8c75da87ec968ae54d314f76a","tid":332167,"uid":3852,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:57:29.000Z","msg":"點煩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日上門搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035c24800a8ef3864a1cb893858ad4b467abbd4a","tid":332167,"uid":81684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺, 又樣衰又臭格</blockquote><br />\n咁你屋企啲女人咪仲撚樣衰？"},{"pid":"00c7125ca0ef9be4bef51bafa917a91730a56499","tid":332167,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"182a8203964135bc95a1b4fbb380f8449f768b36","tid":332167,"uid":84465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:33:43.000Z","msg":"啲記者到而家都仲問林作咪仲煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e1bd1d1090868ae8349d4c59abaded0ef30d9a","tid":332167,"uid":45170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"唔覺！"},{"pid":"c0e0476d2848ad290b0e28c1be1021843e675145","tid":332167,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"吳國！"},{"pid":"653a0507d31e698ddf917d335f7e7c786c834496","tid":332167,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea600dff65bd3cec83b856f1b4d72d41da1633c8","tid":332167,"uid":18663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"唔覺"}]}